-- Tokyo's Nikkei share average closes down 6.18 percent
-- 
-- Mon Mar 14, 2011 3:36am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/14/us-markets-japan-idUSTRE72D03K20110314

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Japan's benchmark Nikkei average  .N225  closed down 6.18 percent at 9,620.49 on Monday, while the broader Topix  .TOPX  shed 7.49 percent to 846.96. 

 (Reporting by Tokyo markets team)